    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/231551089a58c73560c3db2881efc5d5.poster.avif?t=1760188845\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/231551089a58c73560c3db2881efc5d5.webm?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/231551089a58c73560c3db2881efc5d5.mp4?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>immersiX, blending art and science</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ImmersiX is a multi-content app poised to revolutionize visual storytelling across any Open XR headset. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ImmersiX seamlessly blends the creative essence of immersion with the scientific power of six degrees of freedom (6DoF), bridging the worlds of art, science, and technology in ways never seen before. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/74bbb1403cd4bc8b35e99350d891a319.poster.avif?t=1760188845\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/74bbb1403cd4bc8b35e99350d891a319.webm?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/74bbb1403cd4bc8b35e99350d891a319.mp4?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This next-generation app not only showcases original movies from V-Nova Studios, but also opens the door for third-party creators to add their own immersive experiences, making ImmersiX a dynamic hub for world-class XR storytelling. Audiences are transported beyond imagination, exploring breathtaking worlds with complete freedom and presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/8c9ea035266074d00b8b28bc141efe21.poster.avif?t=1760188845\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/8c9ea035266074d00b8b28bc141efe21.webm?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704450/extras/8c9ea035266074d00b8b28bc141efe21.mp4?t=1760188845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powered by the groundbreaking V-Nova PresenZ format, ImmersiX delivers hyper-realistic visuals, offering an unprecedented, authentic, sense of movement and detail that rivals reality itself. Coupled with spatial audio, the experience becomes truly lifelike, pushing the boundaries of what is possible in entertainment and technology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ImmersiX is more than an experience — it is a new frontier in storytelling, where viewers don’t just watch— they feel, explore, and connect like never before. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
